		    quid       	"3DB5077C015A"
		    documentation 	
|DESCRIPTION
|Moves the motor to the given position using the absolute scale.
|All distances and positions are in steps
|
|PARAMETERS
|p_iTargetPosition: target position where the motor will drive to
|p_iSearchDistance: distance before target position is reached where the motor will drive using the search speed
|
|RETURNS
|async void
|
		    
		    stereotype 	"pure virtual"
		    parameters 	(list Parameters
			(object Parameter "p_iTargetPosition"
			    type       	"INT")
			(object Parameter "p_iSearchDistance"
			    type       	"INT"
			    initv      	"0"))
		    result     	"CCOSyncObject*"
		    concurrency 	"Sequential"
		    opExportControl 	"Public"
		    uid        	1035273349)
		(object Operation "MoveRelative"
		    attributes 	(list Attribute_Set
			(object Attribute
			    tool       	"cg"
			    name       	"cg_style"
			    value      	"Pure Virtual"))
		    quid       	"3DB507D603AC"
		    documentation 	
|DESCRIPTION
|Moves the motor the given distance relative to the current position
|All distances and positions are in steps
|
|PARAMETERS
|p_iTotalDistance:  relative distance the motor will move
|p_iSearchDistance: distance before target position is reached where the motor will drive using the search speed
|
|RETURNS
|async void
|
		    
		    stereotype 	"pure virtual"
		    parameters 	(list Parameters
			(object Parameter "p_iTotalDistance"
			    type       	"INT")
			(object Parameter "p_iSearchDistance"
			    type       	"INT"
			    initv      	"0"))
		    result     	"CCOSyncObject*"
		    concurrency 	"Sequential"
		    opExportControl 	"Public"
		    uid        	1035273350)
		(object Operation "MoveManual"
		    attributes 	(list Attribute_Set
			(object Attribute
			    tool       	"cg"
			    name       	"cg_style"
			    value      	"Pure Virtual"))
		    quid       	"3DB507FE03CB"
		    documentation 	
|DESCRIPTION
|Starts manual moving towards the given end position.
|
|PARAMETERS
|- p_iEndPosition: maximum position of the manual move
|- p_uiSpeed: speed in %
|
|RETURNS
|asynchronous void, signalling that the end position is reached
|
		    
		    stereotype 	"pure virtual"
		    parameters 	(list Parameters
			(object Parameter "p_iEndPosition"
			    type       	"INT")
			(object Parameter "p_uiSpeed"
			    type       	"UINT"))
		    result     	"CCOSyncObject*"
		    concurrency 	"Sequential"
		    opExportControl 	"Public"
		    uid        	1035273351)
